A bolt of lighting struck the ground, from the crater there stood a great 
warrior, ones whos presence has not been felt for some time. With a Blade on 
one hand and his arm cannon on the other. He stood when some had fallen. He 
fought the dinobots to no relentlessness. He is part bull, part hawk, part 
Hammerhead shark. The gods had spoken and Thunder Hammer has returned. He 
looked up and yelled "Aracniaaaaaaa!"
